'''Leavesden Studios''' is situated near [[Wikipedia:Watford|Watford]] in [[Wikipedia:England|England]]. It was the primary filming location of [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']], which started production design in [[August]] [[1996]] with principal photography starting on [[June 26]], [[1997]], and lasting for four weeks. In all, the production used the studio for two and a half years.

